  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·Resource Gathering</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras/2879a55a12a985a860367a40aee30e70.avif?t=1731913771\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras_big/2879a55a12a985a860367a40aee30e70.avif?t=1731913771 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players need to diligently collect various resources, such as wood and ores. Venture deep into dark and dangerous mines, explore every corner of the village and islands, and obtain valuable resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·Crop Cultivation</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras/4cf51b5b76ce724b4b12a5a2d777c373.avif?t=1731913771\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras_big/4cf51b5b76ce724b4b12a5a2d777c373.avif?t=1731913771 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase your favorite crop seeds from merchants, carefully plant and tend to them. Once the crops mature, harvest and process them to boost the village's productivity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·Crafting and Processing</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras/4fa414fbbb85525655da417615f0afac.avif?t=1731913771\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras_big/4fa414fbbb85525655da417615f0afac.avif?t=1731913771 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the collected resources to craft equipment, food, and medicine needed by the villagers. The village also has many processing buildings that can be accessed by unlocking plots, further enhancing production efficiency.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·Building and Upgrading</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras/654bf53637067196548ec04ad1e0b67d.avif?t=1731913771\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras_big/654bf53637067196548ec04ad1e0b67d.avif?t=1731913771 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every villager has a cozy home. Players can upgrade buildings and purchase furniture to create a more comfortable living environment, increasing the villagers' happiness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·Combat</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras/f02ba0f6e73e7db468eacad33291be8e.avif?t=1731913771\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras_big/f02ba0f6e73e7db468eacad33291be8e.avif?t=1731913771 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Goblins and skeletons are lurking in various areas. Defeat these enemies in battle to gain valuable loot and reclaim treasure chests and lands they have occupied, expanding the village's territory.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·Resource Gathering</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras/2879a55a12a985a860367a40aee30e70.avif?t=1731913771\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras_big/2879a55a12a985a860367a40aee30e70.avif?t=1731913771 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players need to diligently collect various resources, such as wood and ores. Venture deep into dark and dangerous mines, explore every corner of the village and islands, and obtain valuable resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·Crop Cultivation</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras/4cf51b5b76ce724b4b12a5a2d777c373.avif?t=1731913771\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras_big/4cf51b5b76ce724b4b12a5a2d777c373.avif?t=1731913771 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase your favorite crop seeds from merchants, carefully plant and tend to them. Once the crops mature, harvest and process them to boost the village's productivity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·Crafting and Processing</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras/4fa414fbbb85525655da417615f0afac.avif?t=1731913771\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras_big/4fa414fbbb85525655da417615f0afac.avif?t=1731913771 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the collected resources to craft equipment, food, and medicine needed by the villagers. The village also has many processing buildings that can be accessed by unlocking plots, further enhancing production efficiency.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·Building and Upgrading</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras/654bf53637067196548ec04ad1e0b67d.avif?t=1731913771\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras_big/654bf53637067196548ec04ad1e0b67d.avif?t=1731913771 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every villager has a cozy home. Players can upgrade buildings and purchase furniture to create a more comfortable living environment, increasing the villagers' happiness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·Combat</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras/f02ba0f6e73e7db468eacad33291be8e.avif?t=1731913771\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189900/extras_big/f02ba0f6e73e7db468eacad33291be8e.avif?t=1731913771 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Goblins and skeletons are lurking in various areas. Defeat these enemies in battle to gain valuable loot and reclaim treasure chests and lands they have occupied, expanding the village's territory.</p>",
